{
  "stem": "942.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were drinks served to these soldiers for two days-- gratis, you know, free drinks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were drinking away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember they were having a real good time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For two solid days, my father was handing out these drinks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember we lived on the-- sort of at the edge of town near the railroad.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because lumber that was brought in from my grandfather, you know, it was close to the railway, so we lived there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had to come into town to school and  to my father's business, and I had to cross the railway-- the railroad.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were the rail guards, you know, when, when a train comes, this post that comes down.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Hungarians put up guards there right away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "For what reason, I really don't know what they were guarding.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But instantly, as soon as he saw me coming, he said, you're a Jew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because, you know, we as Jewish kids, we always wore a cap.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So he could tell right away that I was a Jewish-- I was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So my father prepared little bottles with Schnapps, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And whenever I had to cross, I gave it to the guard, and he let me through without any problem.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we knew that changes were coming in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were now Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had a nanny.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I guess she was like part of the family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She came to our house when I was born.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she practically raised the three of us kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She knew all the Hebrew prayers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And Hungarian laws were-- started almost as soon as the Hungarians came in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the first thing happened that-- within six months, my father's business was taken away from him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Jewish people could not sell any spirits.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
